2. Phenotype query (on Chronicles?) looks at all upcoming appointments for qualification and sets a (smart data element?) 'flag' (at what interval)
3. Human review of report (smart forms?) and then execute the invitation (what is this workflow?)
4. Patient accesses the patient portal where invitation to MyPAIN sits
5. Patient launches MyPAIN
